2019–20 PlusLiga

2018–19 PlusLiga is the 84th season of Polish Championship (20th season as professional league - PlusLiga) organized by Polish Volleyball League SA () under the supervision of Polish Volleyball Federation ().

During PlusLiga season 2018–19 due to Stocznia Szczecin withdrawal from the competition there was no relegation from the league at all.

Ślepsk Suwałki advanced to PlusLiga for the first time in the club's history.

In season 2019–20 eight top-seeded clubs will be qualified for the playoffs.

